title: Chef Dynasty: House of Fang
overview: Chef and restaurateur Kathy Fang serves up mouthwatering Chinese fusion dishes that challenge conventional culinary ideas at Fang, the hot restaurant she co-owns in San Francisco with her father Chef Peter Fang. This father/daughter duo is a dominant force in San Francisco's food world and now Kathy is ready to expand their business while honoring their roots in the docuseries Chef Dynasty: House of Fang.
